Package shape

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Shape
    It is shape interface that Rectangle, Triangle, Circle and Polygon classes implements it.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Circle
    Implements Shape interface as Circle shape.
    ComposedShape
    Fits small shapes inside container shapes.
    Global
    There are three global functions that are used in mainapp.
    Mainapp
    Main class that executes program.
    Polygon
    Implements shape objects helps to draw polygon.
    PolygonDyn
    Extends from Polygon holds data as array.
    PolygonVect
    Extends from Polygon and holds data as arraylist.
    Rectangle
    Implements Shape interface as Rectangle shape.
    Triangle
    Implements Shape interface as Triangle shape.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ShapeException
    Helps to throw exceptions about Shape hierarchy that extends from Exception.
